{"tid":33574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微信傳大亞灣現泄漏事故　第3天才低調封堵泄漏處","createTime":"2016-12-11T01:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T05:23:44.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3150ae46a97630f60e34b26ef34e50d2c64934ef","tid":33574,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:34:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-10-2016/34446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-10-2016%2F34446&d=oViV65MKjtusFbMuXh0bSQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f81ef1f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-10-2016/34446</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/Daya_Bay_Nuclear_Power_Plant.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2FDaya_Bay_Nuclear_Power_Plant.jpg&h=3feb2b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港周邊被中國的多核電廠包圍，其中最令港人關注的廣東大亞灣核電站，有傳上月發生泄漏事件，但當局官方未有證實件，大亞灣網站亦沒有相關事件的報告。<br />\n<br />\n中國微信公號「中國核能」昨日（12月9日）貼文爆料，指大亞灣核電站上月底大修期間發生主泵阻尼器泄漏事件，在廣核設計院核島所牽頭下，由陝西特種橡膠製品公司低調進行封堵項目，該公司在接到任務幾小時內設計出密封方案，並已國家核安全局批准。貼文又指，本月2日完成工裝模具製造、電器控制系統改造、膠圈生產，一天後由公司3名員工，將封堵工具送往大亞灣基地，密封設備則於上周二（11月29日）完成組裝，周日（12月4日）並網發電。據悉，現場操作環境有放射性。<br />\n<br />\n現時負責公司發布的有關消息已被迅速刪除，中國官方及大亞灣網站都沒有披露事件，亦未見中國傳媒報道有關消息。"},{"pid":"1d7e82aada09238570742d8c9b70ea1a7c66f3f0","tid":33574,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b41466c445357b4e58e97636ce9ca90f75c7ec9","tid":33574,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:37:47.000Z","msg":"中國幅射對身體無害<br />\n香港市民可安心享用"},{"pid":"39d8519ad5fc4933687a06c3c89e0741e9e6a326","tid":33574,"uid":63006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:55:45.000Z","msg":"中國的會爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29bcdb18edfc57894737e8f78db6d97d67d5ef3","tid":33574,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:13:14.000Z","msg":"共產黨：再搞港獨就大亞灣核爆，齊齊封地六百年<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaeb46a3d076b97bc2e3a902b6a71ebcf0da373","tid":33574,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:00:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a53ebb608e0c5495cfb726914a63e8b32441d21f","tid":33574,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:23:44.000Z","msg":"核電廠爆有乜所謂 又唔係樓市股市爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}